#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.75"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.75:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.75:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga"
msgstr "8. If You Want"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.75:0.3"
msgid "75. Migasālāsutta"
msgstr "75. With Migasālā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an10.75:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"migasālāya upāsikāya nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane "
"nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"went to the home of the laywoman Migasālā, where he sat on the seat spread "
"out."

msgctxt "an10.75:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho migasālā upāsikā yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho "
"migasālā upāsikā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the laywoman Migasālā went up to Ānanda, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.138"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Kathaṃ kathaṃ nāmāyaṃ, bhante ānanda, bhagavatā dhammo desito aññeyyo, "
"yatra hi nāma brahmacārī ca abrahmacārī ca ubho samasamagatikā bhavissanti "
"abhisamparāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, Ānanda, how on earth are we supposed to understand the teaching taught "
"by the Buddha, when the chaste and the unchaste are both reborn in exactly "
"the same place in the next life?"

#. VAR: ārācārī → anācārī (mr)
msgctxt "an10.75:2.2"
msgid ""
"Pitā me, bhante, purāṇo brahmacārī hoti ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā."
msgstr ""
"My father Purāṇa was celibate, set apart, avoiding the common practice of "
"sex."

msgctxt "an10.75:2.3"
msgid ""
"So kālaṅkato bhagavatā byākato: ‘sakadāgāmī satto tusitaṃ kāyaṃ upapanno’ti."
msgstr ""
"When he passed away the Buddha declared that he was a once-returner, who was "
"reborn in the company of the Joyful Gods."

# See BB for variants.
msgctxt "an10.75:2.4"
msgid "Pitāmaho me, bhante, isidatto abrahmacārī ahosi sadārasantuṭṭho."
msgstr "But my uncle Isidatta was not celibate; he lived content with his wife."

msgctxt "an10.75:2.5"
msgid ""
"Sopi kālaṅkato bhagavatā byākato: ‘sakadāgāmī satto tusitaṃ kāyaṃ "
"upapanno’ti."
msgstr ""
"When he passed away the Buddha declared that he was also a once-returner, "
"who was reborn in the company of the Joyful Gods."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ kathaṃ nāmāyaṃ, bhante ānanda, bhagavatā dhammo desito aññeyyo, yatra "
"hi nāma brahmacārī ca abrahmacārī ca ubho samasamagatikā bhavissanti "
"abhisamparāyan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"How on earth are we supposed to understand the teaching taught by the "
"Buddha, when the chaste and the unchaste are both reborn in exactly the same "
"place in the next life?”"

msgctxt "an10.75:3.2"
msgid "“Evaṃ kho panetaṃ, bhagini, bhagavatā byākatan”ti."
msgstr "“You’re right, sister, but that’s how the Buddha declared it.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando migasālāya upāsikāya nivesane piṇḍapātaṃ gahetvā "
"uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then Ānanda, after receiving almsfood at Migasālā’s house, rose from his "
"seat and left."

msgctxt "an10.75:4.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then after the meal, on his return from alms-round, Ānanda went to the "
"Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"migasālāya upāsikāya nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane "
"nisīdiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:5.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhante, migasālā upāsikā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho, bhante, migasālā "
"upāsikā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.139"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:6.1"
msgid ""
"‘Kathaṃ kathaṃ nāmāyaṃ, bhante ānanda, bhagavatā dhammo desito aññeyyo, "
"yatra hi nāma brahmacārī ca abrahmacārī ca ubho samasamagatikā bhavissanti "
"abhisamparāyaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:6.2"
msgid ""
"Pitā me, bhante, purāṇo brahmacārī ahosi ārācārī virato methunā gāmadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:6.3"
msgid ""
"So kālaṅkato bhagavatā byākato sakadāgāmī satto tusitaṃ kāyaṃ upapannoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:6.4"
msgid "Pitāmaho me, bhante, isidatto abrahmacārī ahosi sadārasantuṭṭho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:6.5"
msgid ""
"Sopi kālaṅkato bhagavatā byākato—sakadāgāmī satto tusitaṃ kāyaṃ upapannoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:7.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ kathaṃ nāmāyaṃ, bhante ānanda, bhagavatā dhammo desito aññeyyo, yatra "
"hi nāma brahmacārī ca abrahmacārī ca ubho samasamagatikā bhavissanti "
"abhisamparāyan’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:7.2"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhante, migasālaṃ upāsikaṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an10.75:7.3"
msgid "‘evaṃ kho panetaṃ, bhagini, bhagavatā byākatan’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: ammakā ammakapaññā → ambakā ambakapaññā (bj) | andhakā andhakapaññā (s1-3) | ambhakā ambhakapaññā (pts1)
msgctxt "an10.75:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Kā cānanda, migasālā upāsikā bālā abyattā ammakā ammakapaññā, ke ca "
"purisapuggalaparopariye ñāṇe?"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, who is this laywoman Migasālā, a foolish incompetent matron, with a "
"matron’s wit? And who is it that knows how to assess individuals?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:9.1"
msgid "Dasayime, ānanda, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "These ten people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an10.75:9.2"
msgid "Katame dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.75:9.3"
msgid "Idhānanda, ekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti."
msgstr "Take a certain person who is unethical."

msgctxt "an10.75:9.4"
msgid ""
"Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, yatthassa taṃ "
"dussilyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"And they don’t truly understand the freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom "
"where that unethical conduct ceases without anything left over."

msgctxt "an10.75:9.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa savanenapi akataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi akataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"appaṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ na labhati."
msgstr ""
"And they’ve not listened or learned or comprehended theoretically or found "
"even temporary freedom."

msgctxt "an10.75:9.6"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā hānāya pareti, no visesāya;"
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re headed for a lower place, "
"not a higher."

msgctxt "an10.75:9.7"
msgid "hānagāmīyeva hoti, no visesagāmī. (1)"
msgstr "They’re going to a lower place, not a higher."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.140"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:10.1"
msgid "Idha panānanda, ekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti."
msgstr "Take a certain person who is unethical."

msgctxt "an10.75:10.2"
msgid ""
"Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti yatthassa taṃ "
"dussilyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"But they truly understand the freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom where "
"that unethical conduct ceases without anything left over."

#. VAR: paṭividdhaṃ → suppaṭividdhaṃ (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an10.75:10.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa savanenapi kataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi kataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"paṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ labhati."
msgstr ""
"And they have listened and learned and comprehended theoretically and found "
"at least temporary freedom."

msgctxt "an10.75:10.4"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā visesāya pareti, no hānāya;"
msgstr ""
