msgctxt "an10.75:20.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa savanenapi kataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi kataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"paṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ labhati."
msgstr ""
"And they’ve listened and learned and comprehended theoretically and found at "
"least temporary freedom."

msgctxt "an10.75:20.4"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā visesāya pareti, no hānāya;"
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re headed for a higher place, "
"not a lower."

msgctxt "an10.75:20.5"
msgid "visesagāmīyeva hoti, no hānagāmī. (8)"
msgstr "They’re going to a higher place, not a lower."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:21.1"
msgid "Tatrānanda, pamāṇikā pamiṇanti … pe …"
msgstr "Judgmental people compare them …"

msgctxt "an10.75:21.2"
msgid "ahaṃ vā, ānanda, puggalesu pamāṇaṃ gaṇheyyaṃ yo vā panassa mādiso."
msgstr "I, or someone like me, may pass judgment on people."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:22.1"
msgid "Idha panānanda, ekacco puggalo uddhato hoti."
msgstr "Take a certain person who is restless."

msgctxt "an10.75:22.2"
msgid ""
"Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti yatthassa taṃ "
"uddhaccaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"And they don’t truly understand the freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom "
"where that restlessness ceases without anything left over."

msgctxt "an10.75:22.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa savanenapi akataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi akataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"appaṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ na labhati."
msgstr ""
"And they’ve not listened or learned or comprehended theoretically or found "
"even temporary freedom."

msgctxt "an10.75:22.4"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā hānāya pareti, no visesāya;"
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re headed for a lower place, "
"not a higher."

msgctxt "an10.75:22.5"
msgid "hānagāmīyeva hoti, no visesagāmī. (9)"
msgstr "They’re going to a lower place, not a higher."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.143"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:23.1"
msgid "Idha panānanda, ekacco puggalo uddhato hoti."
msgstr "Take a certain person who is restless."

msgctxt "an10.75:23.2"
msgid ""
"Tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti yatthassa taṃ "
"uddhaccaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"But they truly understand the freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom where "
"that restlessness ceases without anything left over."

msgctxt "an10.75:23.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa savanenapi kataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi kataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"paṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ labhati."
msgstr ""
"And they’ve listened and learned and comprehended theoretically and found at "
"least temporary freedom."

msgctxt "an10.75:23.4"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā visesāya pareti, no hānāya;"
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re headed for a higher place, "
"not a lower."

msgctxt "an10.75:23.5"
msgid "visesagāmīyeva hoti, no hānagāmī. (10)"
msgstr "They’re going to a higher place, not a lower."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:24.1"
msgid "Tatrānanda, pamāṇikā pamiṇanti:"
msgstr "Judgmental people compare them, saying:"

msgctxt "an10.75:24.2"
msgid ""
"‘imassapi teva dhammā, aparassapi teva dhammā. Kasmā nesaṃ eko hīno eko "
"paṇīto’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘This one has just the same qualities as the other, so why is one worse and "
"one better?’"

msgctxt "an10.75:24.3"
msgid "Tañhi tesaṃ, ānanda, hoti dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "This will be for their lasting harm and suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:25.1"
msgid ""
"Tatrānanda, yvāyaṃ puggalo uddhato hoti tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti yatthassa taṃ uddhaccaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhati, "
msgstr ""
"In this case the person who is restless, but truly understands the freedom "
"of heart … "

msgctxt "an10.75:25.2"
msgid ""
"tassa savanenapi kataṃ hoti, bāhusaccenapi kataṃ hoti, diṭṭhiyāpi "
"paṭividdhaṃ hoti, sāmāyikampi vimuttiṃ labhati."
msgstr ""
"and has listened and learned and comprehended theoretically and found at "
"least temporary freedom"

msgctxt "an10.75:25.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, ānanda, puggalo amunā purimena puggalena abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro "
"ca."
msgstr "is better and finer than the other person."

msgctxt "an10.75:25.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an10.75:25.5"
msgid "Imaṃ hānanda, puggalaṃ dhammasoto nibbahati."
msgstr "Because the stream of the teaching carries them along."

msgctxt "an10.75:25.6"
msgid "Tadantaraṃ ko jāneyya aññatra tathāgatena."
msgstr "But who knows the difference between them except a Realized One?"

msgctxt "an10.75:25.7"
msgid "Tasmātihānanda, mā puggalesu pamāṇikā ahuvattha;"
msgstr "So, Ānanda, don’t be judgmental about people."

msgctxt "an10.75:25.8"
msgid "mā puggalesu pamāṇaṃ gaṇhittha."
msgstr "Don’t pass judgment on people."

msgctxt "an10.75:25.9"
msgid "Khaññati hānanda, puggalesu pamāṇaṃ gaṇhanto."
msgstr "Those who pass judgment on people harm themselves."

msgctxt "an10.75:25.10"
msgid "Ahaṃ vā, ānanda, puggalesu pamāṇaṃ gaṇheyyaṃ yo vā panassa mādiso."
msgstr "I, or someone like me, may pass judgment on people."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:26.1"
msgid ""
"Kā cānanda, migasālā upāsikā bālā abyattā ammakā ammakapaññā, ke ca "
"purisapuggalaparopariye ñāṇe."
msgstr ""
"Who is this laywoman Migasālā, a foolish incompetent matron, with a matron’s "
"wit? And who is it that knows how to assess individuals?"

msgctxt "an10.75:26.2"
msgid "Ime kho, ānanda, dasa puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "These ten people are found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.144"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "an10.75:27.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena, ānanda, sīlena purāṇo samannāgato ahosi tathārūpena sīlena "
"isidatto samannāgato abhavissa, nayidha purāṇo isidattassa gatimpi aññassa."
msgstr ""
"If Isidatta had achieved Purāṇa’s level of ethical conduct, Purāṇa could not "
"have even known Isidatta’s destination."

msgctxt "an10.75:27.2"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpāya cānanda, paññāya isidatto samannāgato ahosi tathārūpāya paññāya "
"purāṇo samannāgato abhavissa, nayidha isidatto purāṇassa gatimpi aññassa."
msgstr ""
"And if Purāṇa had achieved Isidatta’s level of wisdom, Isidatta could not "
"have even known Purāṇa’s destination."

msgctxt "an10.75:27.3"
msgid "Iti kho, ānanda, ime puggalā ubho ekaṅgahīnā”ti."
msgstr "So both individuals were lacking in one respect.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.75:27.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
